lead_paragraph: Ethiopia have appointed former striker Gebremedhin Haile as national coach in the hope he can salvage their faint chances of qualifying for the finals of the African Nations Cup next year.

headline.print_headline: Ethiopia Name Ex-Striker Gebremedhin as National Coach
